    "division-sensors-about": {
      "type": "content-offset",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "heading_small": "Global Intex",
        "heading_large": "Leading the Way in Ruggedized Connectivity and Power Solutions",
        "heading_size": "h1",
        "subheading": "Our Capabilities",
        "content": "<p>Global Intex is at home with the design and construction of heavy-duty ruggedized cable assemblies, low and high-voltage power connectivity solutions and more.  </p><p>After years of experience in the mining and AG sectors, Global Intex is equipped with a specialized engineering staff, dedicated production team and comprehensive manufacturing center. </p><p>The strategic investments from The Paquin Company help this production division thrive by delivering ultra-high-quality products that withstand some of the harshest environments known to man. </p><p>We encourage our customers to challenge us with custom build requirements — <a href=\"/pages/contact\" title=\"Contact\">contact us</a> today to get started.</p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/asset__global-intex--small.jpg",
