    "hero_inline_73QfbR": {
      "type": "hero-inline",
      "name": "Hero [Inline]",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Industries Served",
        "content": "<p>Global Intex connectivity solutions are deployed across some of the most demanding industrial and environmental sectors in the world, including underground and surface mining, onshore and offshore gas and oil, marine and marine deep-sea, agricultural equipment, and subsea research and instrumentation. Each of these environments presents unique combinations of mechanical stress, chemical exposure, moisture, pressure, and temperature extremes. Global Intex products are engineered specifically to meet those conditions head-on, not just survive them.</p>",
        "cta_primary_text": "Contact Us",
